import React from 'react' import { Container, Nav, Navbar, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap' import ReadDataset from './ReadDataset' const ChooseDataset = ({ title }) => { const { dataLoaded, datasetData } = ReadDataset() return (
{title}
{dataLoaded && datasetData.map((file, index) => ( {file} ))}
) } export default ChooseDataset
